{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, ICAA includes Code-Intention Consistency Checking, which ensures the code aligns with the developer's intended functionality by analyzing code comments, documentation, and variable names.",
    "Fault Localiztion.",
    "RCAgent [138] performs root cause analysis in cloud environments by using LLM-based agents to collect system data, analyze logs, and diagnose issues.",
    "AgentFL [110] breaks down fault localization into three phases.",
    "The Comprehension Agent identifies potential fault areas, the Navigation Agent narrows down the codebase search, and the Confirmation Agent uses debugging tools to validate the faults."
  ]
}